6
). Aedeagus: penis slightly narrowing to apex, with constriction before bifurcated apex and nearly 8 times as long as wide before bifurcating; parameral appendages thin, long, a little S-like ( fig. 24 a ). Beetles dark brown; pubescence yellowish grey, dual, erect. Length 2.0– 2.5 mm , width 1.1 mm . Mediterranean. ...............................................................
